      <title>OpenAI just pulled the plug on Sora. The same app that went viral for hyper-real...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWS3bZ0jBk1/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655406130_17948136237130808_3539049312694397473_n.heic?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg2MDM5MTUwOTk2NzU2NDc0Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=jnvc7qObdKoQ7kNvwFL0F-d&amp;_nc_oc=AdrzfNO9kB_m9-XNmWvZCceglcXyjmQR5KSXDJ2Ag7CQmZqKZ0AY60IWmHOfiwtpkw4&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=ibSQM3lN9ghcg00Iv8D8hg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwjdcDSUgkEhqN8u7uCDGIEEjY5_78-CdGOZoc2dB70sQ&amp;oe=69C9A013" alt="Instagram billede fra @theartificialintelligence" /></p><p><strong>@theartificialintelligence</strong></p><p>OpenAI just pulled the plug on Sora.<br/>
<br/>
The same app that went viral for hyper-real AI videos…<br/>
Is now being shut down.<br/>
<br/>
Let that sink in.<br/>
<br/>
Sora wasn’t small — it topped the App Store, sparked a wave of AI filmmaking, and pushed generative video into the mainstream.<br/>
<br/>
So why kill it?<br/>
<br/>
Simple: compute and priorities.<br/>
<br/>
OpenAI is shifting away from expensive consumer tools…<br/>
And doubling down on AI that solves real-world problems — especially robotics and world simulation.<br/>
<br/>
Translation:<br/>
Less “AI videos for fun”<br/>
More “AI that interacts with the physical world.”<br/>
<br/>
But that’s not the whole story.<br/>
<br/>
Sora also faced:<br/>
→ Copyright backlash from creators<br/>
→ Concerns over deepfakes &amp; misinformation<br/>
→ Questions about using real people’s likeness<br/>
<br/>
Even a Disney partnership is now reportedly off.<br/>
<br/>
At the same time, competition is heating up:<br/>
→ Anthropic dominating dev tools with Claude<br/>
→ Google pushing aggressive video AI advancements<br/>
<br/>
So OpenAI is making a strategic move:<br/>
<br/>
Cut distractions.<br/>
Focus compute.<br/>
Build the future.<br/>
<br/>
This is a reminder:<br/>
<br/>
In AI, even the most hyped products…<br/>
Can disappear overnight if they don’t fit the bigger vision.<br/>
<br/>
And the real race isn’t content anymore —<br/>
It’s control of intelligence in the real world.<br/>
<br/>
Follo for more AI breakthroughs, tech shifts, and what’s coming next.<br/>
<br/>
#AI #ArtificialIntelligence #OpenAI #Sora #AIVideo</p>]]></description>
